This is the README for the Shabbes Notifier Browser Addon.

How to install
==============
As long as the addon is not registered as a browser addon by Mozilla, it may be installed as a Temporary Extension as follows (tested with Firefox 56):
1. Pull the code from Github.
2. Open Firefox and type in the url: about:debugging.
3. Click the Load Temporary Add-on button.
4. Browse to the root of the source code pulled on step 1 and choose any file within it and click Open.
5. You should see a headline "Temporary Extensions" and Shabbes Notifier listed beneath it.
